<h2 id="computer-and-program">Computer and Program</h2>

<p>CPU:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Run program</li>
  <li>Process data</li>
</ul>

<p>Memory:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Hold program</li>
  <li>Hold data</li>
</ul>

<p>I/O:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Persist data</li>
  <li>Communication</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="operating-system-revolution">Operating System Revolution</h2>

<p>1935 -1938: Z1mechanical computer by Zuse, Germany</p>

<p><img src="https://hazel-new.github.io/HazelBlog//images/Linux/1.jpg" alt="book" /></p>

