<p>1944: Colossus</p>

<p><img src="https://hazel-new.github.io/HazelBlog//images/Linux/3.jpg" alt="book" /></p>

<p>1946: Public unveiling of ENIAC electronic computer</p>

<p><img src="https://hazel-new.github.io/HazelBlog//images/Linux/4.jpg" alt="book" /></p>

<p>1948: First RAM-stored program from university of Manchester</p>

<p><img src="https://hazel-new.github.io/HazelBlog//images/Linux/5.jpg" alt="book" /></p>

<p>1949: Birth of Modem, computers talk over phone lines</p>

